text: Alex Konstantinou (born 11 April 1992) is a Cypriot professional football player. He plays as a winger for Pafos. He is the son of Kostakis Konstantinou, retired Cyprus national football team player. == Other websites == *APOEL official profile * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Cypriot sportspeople Category:European footballers Category:Nicosia
